:QUOTE [subtitle:James Clear, quotetype:PLAIN]
You do not rise to the level of your goals. You fall to the level of your systems.

:JOURNEY
Reading Atomic Habits
Section
Usefulness
- Opening chapters | 2 | Blog in disguise | Felt like productivity content dressed up
- Identity chapter | 5 | Game changer | Single reframe changed how I saw all habits
- Habit stacking | 4 | Dense but worth it | Examples eventually worked on me
- Final third | 4 | Honest and practical | Clear about what habit systems cannot fix

